it is really several fold.

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:40.901
The first is that it's dominant.

00:03:41.441 --> 00:03:45.103
It's presented in great detail in Shamuw'el,

00:03:45.483 --> 00:03:47.403
listen to God, two Samuel,

00:03:48.283 --> 00:03:49.084
eleven and twelve.

00:03:50.504 --> 00:03:54.326
And the events that follow and really

00:03:55.526 --> 00:03:59.188
thirteen through twenty something are all

00:03:59.209 --> 00:04:03.092
a derivative of this so it's pervasive in

00:04:03.111 --> 00:04:05.394
the text God didn't turn away from it

00:04:06.555 --> 00:04:08.795
and we have never run from anything in

00:04:08.855 --> 00:04:10.717
the twenty four years we have done this

00:04:11.718 --> 00:04:14.920
we've though picked our battles so that we

00:04:14.961 --> 00:04:17.023
turn to them at their proper time and

00:04:17.083 --> 00:04:18.783
i think this is now the proper time

00:04:19.805 --> 00:04:22.086
after we have burnished those resume and

00:04:22.107 --> 00:04:24.389
appropriately so for us to

00:04:26.017 --> 00:04:30.160
