She wept, mourning over her Ba'al,

00:08:47.409 --> 00:08:48.190
Lord and Master.

00:08:50.932 --> 00:08:55.394
It never suggests that she knows that he

00:08:55.433 --> 00:08:58.434
was murdered or that Dowd was the one

