who committed the crime.

00:09:03.557 --> 00:09:07.339
When the 'ebel, the ceremonial,

00:09:08.370 --> 00:09:13.812
morning ritual had passed.

00:09:13.831 --> 00:09:17.013
Then Dowd sent out and he, 'asaph,

